data.description:
Introducing a one-of-a-kind custom log home, a true masterpiece of craftsmanship and natural beauty. This remarkable residence is nestled on a sprawling 2.3-acre parcel of land, offering a serene and picturesque escape from the hustle and bustle of city life.

As you approach this stunning property, you'll be greeted by the warm and inviting exterior constructed from yellow pine hand-hued logs. The rustic charm and character of this log home are immediately evident, making it a unique and timeless retreat.

With over 2200 square feet of meticulously designed living space, this home provides ample room for comfortable living and entertaining. The interior boasts a thoughtful layout, featuring three spacious bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms.

The heart of this home is the open-concept living area, where the grandeur of the log construction is on full display. A cozy fireplace adds warmth and ambiance, creating the perfect setting for gatherings with friends and family. Large windows and a soaring ceiling flood the space with natural light and frame the breathtaking panoramic views that will leave you in awe.

The master bedroom is a sanctuary of relaxation, offering a private retreat with an en-suite bathroom and serene vistas. The remaining bedrooms are equally inviting, with plenty of space for rest and rejuvenation.

The 2.3 acres of land provide ample room for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the peaceful surroundings while spending time in your pool. The country setting offers tranquility and a sense of seclusion, yet you're just minutes away from downtown Kingsport, ensuring convenience and access to all the amenities the city has to offer.

This custom log home is a rare find, a harmonious blend of natural elegance, craftsmanship, and modern comfort. If you're seeking a home that offers a unique and idyllic lifestyle, this property is a must-see. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional residence your own!
